title: Concord View Condo with Air Conditioning opposite Sculpture Park -
posting_body: ['Concord Condos with Air Conditioning across from the Sculpture Park in Belltown with breathtaking of Elliott Bay, the Olympic Mountains, Bainbridge Island and West Seattle.', 'Unit features: air conditioning, a balcony, kitchen bistro bar, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances, gas fireplace, bedroom with walk-in closet and custom shelving, gas heat, limestone kitchen/bath/entry and W/D. Building has concrete and steel construction that help mitigate neighbor noises typically found in apartments with wooden floor structure.', 'Common area features: 24 hour concierge, a business center, lounge (full kitchen, dining area, cable TV/media area), exercise room, high speed Internet, spa, sauna and guest unit for rent and board room for reserve.', 'Common area items in photos may vary.', 'Notes:', 'Rent year 1 = $2,325; Water/Sewer/Garbage/Gas/Garage parking(1)= $300.', 'Parking can be sublet if desired.', 'Rent year 2 option, $2,425.', 'No smoking.', 'No pets.', 'Fully refundable security deposit $2400.', 'Approx.', '$500 Concord Condo HOA move in fee payable to the HOA.', 'Credit Check <URL> $55-$65', 'Reusable tenant screening report not accepted.']
